<suppressions xmlns="https://jeremylong.github.io/DependencyCheck/dependency-suppression.1.3.xsd">
	<suppress>
		<notes><![CDATA[
   The quarkus-openapi-generator-server-2.14.0-lts.jar is a code-generation-only dependency:
   it produces the Java classes and REST APIs of the io.openk9.enrichers module
   from internally defined OpenAPI specifications. The resulting APIs are generated
   source code and have no relation to the /api/gen/clients/{language} endpoint
   referenced in CVE-2023-27162.
   ]]></notes>
		<filePath regex="true">.*quarkus-openapi-generator-server-.*\.jar.*</filePath>
		<cve>CVE-2023-27162</cve>
	</suppress>
</suppressions>